The result should be a a method on CaseCreationWizardPage as follows:

	/**
	 * Selects the specified case type from the choose case type list view, and clicks the next button. This then returns the expected destination page
	 * 
	 * @param caseTypeName
	 *            The name of the case type to select
	 * @param nextPageClass
	 *            The expected destination page class
	 * @return The expected destination page
	 */
	public &lt;T extends Header&gt; T selectCaseTypeAndClickNext(String caseTypeName, Class&lt;T&gt; nextPageClass) {
		ChooseCaseTypeListview.selectRowAndWaitForStaleness(caseTypeName);
		return nextButton.click(nextPageClass);
	}

